metadata.name: Andrea
metadata.description:
Andrea hints at our aspiration to combine human and non-human life in a balanced and uncompromised way. A form of coexistence. 
Andrea reminds us that we are all 'Part of Nature' and we must work to live in harmony with the ecosystem. 
The 'Coexisting' collection explores the relationship between the body and nature in a series of 1/1 female portraits.
